<section  class="l-section">
      <div  class="l-constrain l-constrain--large">
  
  
  <div class="l-section__content">
                    <h2 class="c-featured-cards__title">Exhibits</h2>
    
    <div class="c-featured-cards__content">
              <div class="c-featured-cards__feature">
                    
<div  class="c-card  c-card--feature">
  
  <div class="c-card__body">
    <div class="c-card__header">
            <h3 class="c-card__title">
                <a href="/explore/exhibitions/more-perfect-union">
                    A More Perfect Union
                  </a>
              </h3>
              <h4 class="c-card__subtitle">
          Japanese Americans and the U.S. Constitution
        </h4>
          </div>
          <div class="c-card__content">
        A More Perfect Union: Japanese Americans and the U.S. Constitution traced the history of Japanese American confinement from immigration in the late 19th century to court cases and redress that came more than 40 years after the camps closed in 1946.

              </div>
    
          <div class="c-card__footer">
                        
        
                  <div class="c-card__meta">
                                              </div>
        
              </div>
      </div>

      <div class="c-card__media">
      <div class="c-card__media-inner">
                  <img src="/sites/default/files/styles/card/public/exhibitions/a_more_perfect_b.jpg?itok=9Bq3vFnT" alt="A More Perfect Union" typeof="foaf:Image" />

              </div>
    </div>
  </div>
        </div>
                  

<div  class="l-grid l-grid--3-col">
                                  
<div  class="c-card">
      <div class="c-card__media">
      <div class="c-card__media-inner">
                  <img src="/sites/default/files/styles/card/public/exhibitions/EO9066_b.jpg?itok=0y2mjULu" alt="Collage of objects and images featured in 9066" typeof="foaf:Image" />

              </div>
    </div>
  
  <div class="c-card__body">
    <div class="c-card__header">
            <h3 class="c-card__title">
                <a href="/explore/exhibitions/righting-wrong-japanese-americans-and-world-war-ii">
                    Righting a Wrong
                  </a>
              </h3>
              <h4 class="c-card__subtitle">
           Japanese Americans and World War II
        </h4>
          </div>
          <div class="c-card__content">
        The exhibition explored Japanese American history through the Executive Order 9066 document on loan from the National Archives; original artwork by Roger Shimomura, who spent several years in the Minidoka camp in Idaho; historic images; and objects.

              </div>
    
          <div class="c-card__footer">
                        
        
                  <div class="c-card__meta">
                                                  <div class="c-card__icon c-card__online">
                <span>Online</span>
              </div>
                      </div>
        
              </div>
      </div>

  </div>
                            
<div  class="c-card">
      <div class="c-card__media">
      <div class="c-card__media-inner">
                  <img src="/sites/default/files/styles/card/public/exhibitions/header.jpg?itok=zC8_iKfi" alt="Congressional Gold Medal" typeof="foaf:Image" />

              </div>
    </div>
  
  <div class="c-card__body">
    <div class="c-card__header">
            <h3 class="c-card__title">
                <a href="/explore/exhibitions/american-heroes">
                    American Heroes
                  </a>
              </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="c-card__content">
        In spite of this forced incarceration and rampant wartime prejudice, more than 33,000 second-generation Japanese Americans (nisei) volunteered to serve in the U.S. Army during World War II.

              </div>
    
          <div class="c-card__footer">
                        
        
                  <div class="c-card__meta">
                                              </div>
        
              </div>
      </div>

  </div>
              
  </div>

          </div>
  
      </div>

      </div>
  </section>
</div>


  </div>




  
  
  
  

      </div>

  
  </main>

    


      
